{
  "video_id": "z9sa2ZAqHl0",
  "title": "Robin Ince: Science versus wonder?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to apologize, first of all, to all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "because I have no form"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "of PowerPoint presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "So what I&#39;m going to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "is, every now and again, I will make this gesture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "and in a moment of PowerPoint democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "you can imagine what you&#39;d like to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "I do a radio show."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "The radio show is called \"The Infinite Monkey Cage.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about science, it&#39;s about rationalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "So therefore, we get a lot of complaints"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "every single week --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "complaints including one we get very often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "which is to say the very title, \"Infinite Monkey Cage,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "celebrates the idea of vivisection."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "We have made it quite clear to these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "that an infinite monkey cage is roomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "We also had someone else who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "\"&#39;The Infinite Monkey Cage&#39; idea is ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "An infinite number of monkeys"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "could never write the works of Shakespeare."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "We know this because they did an experiment.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Yes, they gave 12 monkeys a typewriter for a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "and after a week, they only used it as a bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "So the main element though, the main complaint we get --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "and one that I find most worrying --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "is that people say, \"Oh, why do you insist"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "on ruining the magic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "You bring in science, and it ruins the magic.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m an arts graduate;"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "I love myth and magic"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "and existentialism and self-loathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "But I also don&#39;t understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "how it does ruin the magic."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "All of the magic, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "that may well be taken away by science"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "is then replaced by something as wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "Astrology, for instance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "like many rationalists, I&#39;m a Pisces."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "Now astrology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "we remove the banal idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "that your life could be predicted;"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;ll, perhaps today, meet a lucky man"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s wearing a hat."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "That is gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "But if we want to look at the sky and see predictions, we still can."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "We can see predictions of galaxies forming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "of galaxies colliding into each other, of new solar systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "This is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "If the Sun could one day -- and indeed the Earth, in fact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "if the Earth could read its own astrological, astronomical chart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "one day it would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "\"Not a good day for making plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll been engulfed by a red giant.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "And that to me as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "that if you think I&#39;m worried about losing worlds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "well Many Worlds theory --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "one of the most beautiful, fascinating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "sometimes terrifying ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "from the quantum interpretation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "That every person here, every decision that you&#39;ve made today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "every decision you&#39;ve made in your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve not really made that decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "but in fact, every single permutation of those decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "is made, each one going off into a new universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "That is a wonderful idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "If you ever think that your life is rubbish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "always remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s another you that&#39;s made much worse decisions than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "If you ever think, \"Ah, I want to end it all,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t end it all."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "Remember that in the majority of universes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t even exist in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "This to me, in its own strange way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "is very, very comforting."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "Now reincarnation, that&#39;s another thing gone -- the afterlife."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "Science actually says"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "we will live forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "Well, there is one proviso."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "We won&#39;t actually live forever. You won&#39;t live forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "Your consciousness, the you-ness of you, the me-ness of me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "that gets this one go."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "But every single thing that makes us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "every atom in us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "has already created a myriad of different things"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "and will go on to create a myriad of new things."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "We have been mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "and apples and pulsars"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "and other people&#39;s knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "Who knows, maybe one of your atoms was once Napoleon&#39;s knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "That is a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "Unlike the occupants of the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "the universe itself is not wasteful."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "We are all totally recyclable."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "And when we die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t even have to be placed in different refuse sacs."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "This is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "Understanding, to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "does not remove the wonder and the joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "For instance, my wife could turn to me and she may say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "\"Why do you love me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "And I can with all honesty"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "look her in the eye and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "\"Because our pheromones"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "matched our olfactory receptors.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "Though I&#39;ll probably also say something"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "about her hair and personality as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "And that is a wonderful thing there."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "Love does not die because of that thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "Pain doesn&#39;t go away either."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "This is a terrible thing, even though I understand pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "If someone punches me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "and because of my personality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "this is recently a regular occurrence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "I understand where the pain comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 312260.0,
      "text": "It is basically momentum to energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "where the four-vector is constant -- that&#39;s what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "But at no point can I react and go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "\"Ha! Is that the best momentum-to-energy fourth vector constant you&#39;ve got?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "No, I just spit out a tooth."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "And that is all of these different things -- the love for my child."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "I have a son. His name is Archie."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m very lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "because he&#39;s better than all the other children."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "Now I know you don&#39;t think that."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "You may well have your own children"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "and think, \"Oh no, my child&#39;s best.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the wonderful thing about evolution --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "the predilection to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "that our child is best."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "Now in many ways, that&#39;s just a survival thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "The fact we see here is the vehicle for our genes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "and therefore we love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t notice that bit; we just unconditionally love."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "That is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "Though I should say that my son is best"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 365260.0,
      "text": "and is better than your children."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve done some tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "And all of these things to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "give such joy and excitement and wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "Even quantum mechanics can give you an excuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "for bad housework, for instance."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "Perhaps you&#39;ve been at home for a week on your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "You house is in a terrible state."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "Your partner is about to return."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "You think, what should I do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "Do nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "All you have to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "is, when she walks in, using a quantum interpretation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "say, \"I&#39;m so sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "I stopped observing the house for a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "and when I started observing again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "everything had happened.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the strong anthropic principle of vacuuming."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "For me, it&#39;s a very, very important thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "Even on my journey up here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "the joy that I have on my journey up here every single time."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "If you actually think, you remove the myth and there is still something wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sitting on a train."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "Every time I breathe in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m breathing in a million-billion-billion"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "atoms of oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sitting on a chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "Even though I know the chair is made of atoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "and therefore actually in many ways empty space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "I find it comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "I look out the window, and I realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "that every single time we stop and I look out that window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "framed in that window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "wherever we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "I am observing more life"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "than there is in the rest of the known universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "beyond the planet Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "If you go to the safari parks"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "on Saturn or Jupiter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "you will be disappointed."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "And I realize I&#39;m observing this"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "with the brain, the human brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "the most complex thing in the known universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "That, to me, is an incredible thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "And do you know what, that might be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "Steven Weinberg, the Nobel laureate, once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "\"The more the universe seems comprehensible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "the more it seems pointless.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "Now for some people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "that seems to lead to an idea of nihilism."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "But for me, it doesn&#39;t. That is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m glad the universe is pointless."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "It means if I get to the end of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "the universe can&#39;t turn to me and go, \"What have you been doing, you idiot?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not the point.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "I can make my own purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "You can make your own purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "We have the individual power"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "to go, \"This is what I want to do.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "And in a pointless universe, that, to me, is a wonderful thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "I have chosen to make silly jokes"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "about quantum mechanics and the Copenhagen interpretation."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "You, I imagine, can do much better things with your time."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. Goodbye."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}